{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "title": "Loki Logs Dashboard",
    "tags": ["kubernetes", "loki", "logs", "monitoring"],
    "style": "dark",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Log Volume by Namespace",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=\"kubernetes-pods\"}[5m])) by (namespace)",
            "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {"label": "Log Lines/sec"}
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0}
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Log Volume by Pod",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=\"kubernetes-pods\"}[5m])) by (pod)",
            "legendFormat": "{{pod}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {"label": "Log Lines/sec"}
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0}
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Error Logs by Application",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=\"kubernetes-pods\", level=\"error\"}[5m])) by (app)",
            "legendFormat": "{{app}} - Errors"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {"label": "Error Logs/sec"}
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8}
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Warning Logs by Application",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=\"kubernetes-pods\", level=\"warn\"}[5m])) by (app)",
            "legendFormat": "{{app}} - Warnings"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {"label": "Warning Logs/sec"}
        ],
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8}
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Log Query Examples",
        "type": "text",
        "content": "## Sample Log Queries\n\n**All logs from a specific namespace:**\n```\n{namespace=\"monitoring\"}\n```\n\n**Error logs from all pods:**\n```\n{job=\"kubernetes-pods\"} |= \"error\"\n```\n\n**Logs containing specific text:**\n```\n{job=\"kubernetes-pods\"} |= \"connection refused\"\n```\n\n**Logs from specific time range:**\n```\n{job=\"kubernetes-pods\"} [5m]\n```",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16}
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Loki Status",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"loki\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Loki Service"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {
              "mode": "thresholds"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                {"color": "green", "value": 1}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 24}
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "Log Storage Usage",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "loki_build_info",
            "legendFormat": "Loki Version"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 24}
      }
    ],
    "time": {
      "from": "now-1h",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "refresh": "30s"
  }
}
